title: Cafe Grunowksi
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Fast food, Beer/Wine, German, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. An alternative pub and restaurant located close to Schiller's former house in the centre of Jena. It has a large garden in which you can eat and drink, and an extensive menu. The vegan options are not listed explicitly, so ask. Live music sometimes.
